title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA! Mike Florio, Lavelle E Neal III, Paul Charchian, Pat Micheletti
description: Nordo fills in for PA, Mike Florio talks all things NFL to open the show, we run through Dan Bailey’s greatest hits, Lavelle E Neal III checks in from Spring Training in Florida, Paul Charchian talks VR headsets and plenty of football, and Pat Micheletti joins to talk Wild and Gophers Hockey, and even some Wolves.
